RE Start DateDana Thanks for the update I did want to let you know that your transfer letter is ready You can stop by my desk at any time to pick it up I am located at EB d Thanks Jamie Original Message From Davis Dana Sent Tuesday October AM To Wachel Jamie Subject RE Start Date Good Morning Jamie To attempt to answer your question I can only assume that the transfer date will be November th I did speak to my supervisor yesterday evening and she spoke with our director but I still have not been able to confirm this date My supervisor is out this morning but will be back in by noon I should have a definite answer for you after lunch If you have any questions please call me Thanks Dana Original Message From Wachel Jamie Sent Monday October PM To Davis Dana Subject Start Date Dana I was wondering if you have set a transfer date yet Please let me know so I can relay the information to Bill Hare Thanks Jamie EWS Staffing ext
